515
01:05:11,820 --> 01:05:13,600
Oh!

516
01:05:33,510 --> 01:05:34,790
Whoa!

517
01:05:36,680 --> 01:05:38,960
Whoo-hoo!

518
01:06:11,680 --> 01:06:13,090
Whoo!

519
01:06:22,760 --> 01:06:24,100
Whoa.

520
01:06:41,880 --> 01:06:43,690
Wow.

521
01:06:54,560 --> 01:06:57,830
Gần tới nơi rồi.
